data.description: House hunters - rates are improving and this is a Luxury Builder: Conner Homes a must see Contemporary. Sought after Westridge View neighborhood, excellent schools. Modern 4-bedroom home, that backs the greenbelt with upgrades: engineered plank floors, granite countertops, spacious 3-level executive home.  The main level open living space with the Cook's kitchen, large island, and walk-in pantry lend this home to entertaining and gathering.  Walls of windows! Ready to relax, ascend the staircase to the primary suite!  Upper and lower level bedrooms. Valley, mountain, territorial views. Multiple neighborhood parks, sports court, dog park, trails schools, shopping, and restaurants. Easy commute. Welcome home. New Garage door!
